{"tid":2499874,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個做毒撚最慘嘅事","createTime":"2021-04-22T08:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T08:40:56.000Z","uid":307910,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8dde47c27849ce29222fdf28af6a2f15c94d92d1","tid":2499874,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"喺好多年前，有套日本動畫叫你的名字，咁喺香港大熱，香港好多戲院都上咗呢類畫風嘅日本動畫，咁有一套就叫唔知乜春嘢煙花應該和誰看，咁有一次見冇嘢做搵咗個星期日自己入場睇啦，然之後，問題就嚟<br />\n<br />\n成個戲院入面，一個好似我咁嘅毒撚都冇，全部都係一pair pair嘅情侶，我記得當日個場好爆，入到未熄燈之前已經五六成滿，幾十對眼就望住我一個孤伶伶嘅死毒撚去睇呢套青春愛情動畫<br />\n<br />\n我真係睇得好kick，周圍嘅情侶都上下其手，又攬又錫<br />\n<br />\n唯獨我一個死毒撚，想睇戲都專心唔到，比隔離左右嘈住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完場嘅時候，我因為唔想比啲情侶塞住，播歌出製作名單嗰一秒已經跑咗出戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我發誓，我以後只會睇早場戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為得啲阿叔呀嬸貪平睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔會再有人借睇戲巢下巢下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d10f42f2ee704066ec8ac9a0cb4b4fe99eb3876","tid":2499874,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"或者嗰時應該約kelly<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢一定會笑我死毒撚 唔比我date<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86819332b2649ebb9def4a15ec0ad97dc1377444","tid":2499874,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5zY9kVM3xQ&amp;t=1204s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK5zY9kVM3xQ%26t%3D1204s&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=7180d250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5zY9kVM3xQ&amp;t=1204s</a><br />\n孤獨死 編號墓碑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f45e079996bf5666ba89eb27e2c4a257dc211e","tid":2499874,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86819332b2649ebb9def4a15ec0ad97dc1377444","tid":2499874,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5zY9kVM3xQ&amp;t=1204s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK5zY9kVM3xQ%26t%3D1204s&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=7180d250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5zY9kVM3xQ&amp;t=1204s</a><br />\n孤獨死 編號墓碑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}